{{! About Us Section }}
<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center text-light">
      <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        The Sustainability Cooperative at the University of Maryland, fondly known as SCoop,
        is a collective of student organizations interested in improving sustainability on campus.
        Founded by students in 2018, SCoop continues to grow and host more opportunities for
        members of our community and for the larger university and city. By joining together,
        we optimize funding opportunities, and individual SCoop member organizations gain an
        advantage in building interdisciplinary project teams. The cooperative meets regularly
        to network and workshop concepts and projects, allowing for increased collaboration and
        innovation as well as elevated awareness of local initiatives!
      </p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScmATvxlUGnK4E7SJfmPFcy5yp5WRuZP0yC6-LNumfIgckWsQ/viewform?usp=sf_link" type="" class="btn btn-outline-light mr-3"><span class="fas fa-user-plus icon-left"></span> Become a Member</a>
      <a href="http://eepurl.com/gmHjcT" type="" class="btn btn-outline-light mr-3"><span class="fas fa-mail-bulk icon-left"></span> Join Our Email List</a>
      <a href="mailto:scoopumd@gmail.com" type="" class="btn btn-outline-light"><span class="far fa-envelope icon-left"></span> Email Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="container text-light">
    <div class="row text-center justify-content-center">
